Articles.Content: Landing on Duna discord server: https://discord.gg/4d7PSyG

Nice Video,GabrielP.

Suggestion:you should wait for Kerbin to get it Near to Duna before Launching,you could also convert your Lander into a Base that can Refuel it self with an ISRU Part,ore Extractor and ore containers,which it could take hundred of days,depending on how powerfull it is,after Refueling,wait again for Kerbin and Duna to get Near(the  Node would be the same like going to Eve),then Takeoff from Duna to go to Kerbin,Aerobrake at an altitude of 55KM,after the Orbit Capture,re-aerobrake at an altitude of 40KM(this will succesfully bring your Vessel to the ground) and Celebrate your Victory.
